nodes.text: Bottom-feeder gumbo was a sticky, black, acrid stuff with nameless floating pale blobs that were the color of tree lichen. It smelled extraordinarily like burning lubricant. It was made of mixed vegetables and otherwise useless fish. It only appealed to a small number of beings, Jedi Master Yoda among them.
It was served by Fidelis to Yoda aboard the Nighthawk.
